```plantuml
@startuml
title 学生列表用例时序图

actor teacher
participant "courseClass" as courseClass
participant "S_C" as S_C
participant "student" as student
participant "experimentscores" as experimentscores
participant "cexperiments" as cexperiments
participant "experimentclauses" as experimentclauses

teacher ->> courseClass : 根据工号以及默认学期获取\n所授课程开课班号及课程号
activate courseClass
courseClass ->> S_C : 获取学生成绩及学号
activate S_C
S_C ->> student : 获取学生信息
activate student
student --> S_C : 每个所授学生信息及其已批改实验平均成绩列表
deactivate student
S_C --> courseClass
deactivate S_C
courseClass --> teacher
deactivate courseClass

rectangle {
    note left: 点击成绩详情
    teacher ->> experimentscores : 根据学号,课程号开课班号查找试实验成绩单号
    activate experimentscores
    experimentscores ->> cexperiments : 获取实验及成绩信息
    activate cexperiments
    cexperiments ->> experimentclauses : 获取实验及成绩信息
    activate experimentclauses
    experimentclauses --> cexperiments
    deactivate experimentclauses
    cexperiments --> experimentscores
    deactivate cexperiments
    experimentscores --> teacher : 返回所点击学生该课程所有相关实验成绩列表
    deactivate experimentscores
}

@enduml
```